    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep luster and no chips, scratches, or dings of any kind. Inside, the leather is soft and supple, the carpets are spotless, and all electronics function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is sound, offering a smooth and powerful driving experience that feels brand new. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle that has been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment.",
